    <string name="f_about_title">About me</string>
    <string name="f_about_text">Hi, \n\nThanks for trying out my app! I am an amateur app developer with a life long passion for snooker. I wanted to do something for this sport so I set out to create this app in my spare time. My dream is to improve this app constantly and make it useful to the snooker community, by implementing a login to save all previous matches showing career statistics and adding many new features.\n\nUnfortunately my time and coding skills are not at par with my wishes, so if you feel inspired to help I\'d be glad to share in my efforts. Please send me an e-mail at:</string>
